_:N7e16b2058eb54b7aab5ce45b2e88f058 <http://schema.org/description> "We are an independent panel commissioning reviews of serious child safeguarding cases. We want national and local reviews to focus on improving learning, professional practice and outcomes for children. Child Safeguarding Practice Review Panel works with the Department for Education ." .
